quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,shghlkm ean taeat allah altfakhr bikathrat al'amwal walawlad
  102,2,"wastmr ashtghalkm bdhlk 'iilaa 'ana srtm 'iilaa almqabr, wdufntm fyha"
  102,3,"ma hkdha ynbghy 'an yulhykm altakathur balamwal, sawf ttbyanwn 'ana aldaar alakhirat khayr lkm"
  102,4,thm ahdhru sawf taelamun su' eaqibat anshghalkm enha
  102,5,"ma hkdha ynbghy 'an ylhykm altakathur balamwal, law taelamun haqa aleilm lanzjrtm, wlbadrtm 'iilaa 'iinqadh 'anfusakum min alhlak. ltbsrunn aljhym, thuma ltbsrunnaha dun ryb, thuma ltsalunn yawm alqiamat ean kl 'anwae alneym"
  102,6,"ma hkdha ynbghy 'an ylhykm altakathur balamwal, law taelamun haqa aleilm lanzjrtm, wlbadrtm 'iilaa 'iinqadh 'anfusakum min alhlak. ltbsrunn aljhym, thuma ltbsrunnaha dun ryb, thuma ltsalunn yawm alqiamat ean kl 'anwae alneym"
  102,7,"ma hkdha ynbghy 'an ylhykm altakathur balamwal, law taelamun haqa aleilm lanzjrtm, wlbadrtm 'iilaa 'iinqadh 'anfusakum min alhlak. ltbsrunn aljhym, thuma ltbsrunnaha dun ryb, thuma ltsalunn yawm alqiamat ean kl 'anwae alneym"
  102,8,"ma hkdha ynbghy 'an ylhykm altakathur balamwal, law taelamun haqa aleilm lanzjrtm, wlbadrtm 'iilaa 'iinqadh 'anfusakum min alhlak. ltbsrunn aljhym, thuma ltbsrunnaha dun ryb, thuma ltsalunn yawm alqiamat ean kl 'anwae alneym"